<h3 class=3D"h4 font-title text-dark mb-8" style=3D"scroll-margin-top: 100p=
x" id=3D"submit-form-with-chromedp">Submit Form with Chromedp</h3>
<p class=3D"mb-4">Chromedp allows you to submit a form through the actions.
This all revolves around two functions:</p>
<ul class=3D"mb-4 mt-4 pl-4 list-inside list-disc">
<li><a class=3D"underline hover:text-blue" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopene=
r noreferrer nofollow" href=3D"https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/chromedp/chrom=
edp#SendKeys" style=3D"outline: none;"><code>SendKeys()</code></a>: Action =
that synthesizes the key up, char, and down events to type strings in an in=
put element.</li>
<li><a class=3D"underline hover:text-blue" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopene=
r noreferrer nofollow" href=3D"https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/chromedp/chrom=
edp#Submit" style=3D"outline: none;"><code>Submit()</code></a>: Action that=
 submits the parent form of the first element node matching the selector.
See an example below:</li>
</ul>
           =20
       =20
           =20
       =20
                    <div class=3D"mt-4 code-block-with-header relative" dat=
a-id=3D"content-block__code-header-75">
                <div class=3D"bg-inactive text-gray text-base py-3 px-5 rou=
nded-t-lg">
                    scraper.go
                </div>
       =20
        <div class=3D"mb-8 text-sm " id=3D"_ERoQdbpKOTQNnvt7plg8" data-id=
=3D"content-block__code-75">
            <pre><code class=3D"language-go hljs go" data-lang=3D"go">    e=
rr :=3D chromedp.Run(ctx,
        chromedp.Navigate(<span class=3D"hljs-string">"https://example.org/=
form"</span>),
        chromedp.WaitVisible(sel),
        chromedp.SendKeys(<span class=3D"hljs-string">".name"</span>, <span=
 class=3D"hljs-string">"Maria"</span>),
        chromedp.SendKeys(<span class=3D"hljs-string">".surname"</span>, <s=
pan class=3D"hljs-string">"Williams"</span>),
        <span class=3D"hljs-comment">// filling out the other fields</span>
        chromedp.Submit(<span class=3D"hljs-string">"button[role=3Dsubmit]"=
</span>),
    )
</code></pre>
